cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.RO

This paper deals with the problem of domain adaptation in semantic segmentation of aerial images using Generative Adversarial Networks (GANs). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning methods, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The topic of aerial images and remote sensing could also place it in cs.GR (Graphics) or cs.RO (Robotics).
